docs.lead_paragraph: Many older persons who soon will be eligible for the Federal Medicare program, which goes into effect July 1, are in a quandary as to what they should do with existing health insurance policies, or whether they should buy supplemental insurance.

headline.main: Personal Finance; Many Persons Young and Old Still In a Quandary on Medicare's Benefits QUESTIONS RAISED ON MEDICARE PLAN
